, a facsimile or electronic copy of the shipping record or, if requested, a voice description of the information on the shipping record.::FR_that person or that person’s representative must provide immediately, at the request of a federal, provincial or municipal official including a member of a fire department, a facsimile or electronic copy of the shipping record or, if requested, a voice description of the information on the shipping record.')
