INSERT [dbo].[SOURCE__LEGISLATION] ([(Do Not Modify) Legislation], [(Do Not Modify) Row Checksum], [(Do Not Modify) Modified On], [Name], [Legislation Source], [Parent Legislation], [English Text], [Legislation Type], [Label], [Enabling Act], [Enabling Regulation], [Order], [French Text], [Violation Display Text EN], [Violation Display Text FR], [Violation Text]) VALUES (N'17DF1812-CB13-4FB7-8B5D-4C1CD1AADE82', NULL, NULL, N'TDGR  5.10 (5)', N'Transportation of Dangerous Goods Regulations', N'TDGR  5.10::TMDR  5.10', N'For the purposes of this section, clause 5.1.4 of CSA B340 must be read as requiring a cylinder, sphere or tube that is referred to in subsection (2) that is due for requalification and that does not meet the requirements of the prefill inspection to be rejected and not be filled until the cause for rejection has been corrected.', N'Subsection', N' 5.10 (5)', N'TDGA 5 (d)', NULL, N'335', N'Pour l’application du présent article, l’article 5.1.4 de la norme CSA B340 est interprété comme exigeant que la bouteille à gaz cylindrique ou sphérique ou le tube qui est visé au paragraphe (2), qui doit faire l’objet d’une requalification et qui ne répond pas aux exigences de l’inspection préalable au remplissage soit rejeté et ne soit pas rempli tant que la cause du rejet n’a pas été corrigée.', N'Failing to reject and not fill a cylinder, sphere or tube that is referred to in subsection 10(2) that was due for requalification and that didn''t meet the requirements of the prefill inspection until the cause for rejection had been corrected..', N'Omission de ne pas rejeter et ne pas remplir une bouteille, une sphère ou un tube visé au paragraphe 10 (2) qui devait être requalifié et qui ne répondait pas aux exigences de l''inspection préliminaire avant que la cause du rejet ait été corrigée.', N'For the purposes of this section, clause 5.1.4 of CSA B340 must be read as requiring a cylinder, sphere or tube that is referred to in subsection (2) that is due for requalification and that does not meet the requirements of the prefill inspection to be rejected and not be filled until the cause for rejection has been corrected.::FR_For the purposes of this section, clause 5.1.4 of CSA B340 must be read as requiring a cylinder, sphere or tube that is referred to in subsection (2) that is due for requalification and that does not meet the requirements of the prefill inspection to be rejected and not be filled until the cause for rejection has been corrected.')
GO
