dance with Part 4 (Dangerous Goods Safety Marks) or the IMDG Code.::FR_When dangerous goods are transported in a large means of containment to or from a vessel, a port facility or a marine terminal, the large means of containment must have placards displayed on it in accordance with Part 4 (Dangerous Goods Safety Marks) or the IMDG Code.')
GO
